<H4>    Rabin's Political Statement Approved </H4>

<F P=102> TA1804181894 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1800 GMT 18 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1804181894 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Knesset political debate concluded with 
approval of the prime minister's statement. Our correspondent 
Hayim Hecht reports that the statement was approved by 36 to 28. 
Those who voted for it were the Labor, Meretz, and SHAS [Torah 
Observing Sephardim] factions. 

</TEXT>

