<F P=100> Iran </F>
<H3> <TI>   Car Bomb Explodes in Tehran; Injuries Reported </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Car Bomb Explodes in Tehran; Injuries Reported </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1904090394 Tehran IRNA in English 0848 GMT 19 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1904090394 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran IRNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tehran, April 19, IRNA -- A bomb planted in a car 
parked under an overpass at Tehran's Sa'di Avenue went off 
around noon today, the law enforcement forces told IRNA. 
  The explosion damaged a number of other cars parked near the 
scene of the incident and smashed a large number of window panes 
of nearby shops and homes. 
  Eyewitnesses said that a number of bypassers, including two 
women holding their children in their arms, were injured who 
were rushed to a Tehran hospital. 
  So far no group has assumed responsibility for the 
explosion. 

</TEXT>

