<H3> <TI>   Yerin to 'Arafat: Russia Ready To Help With Police </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yerin to 'Arafat: Russia Ready To Help With Police </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1904175494 Algiers Voice of Palestine in Arabic 1702 GMT 
19 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1904175494 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Voice of Palestine </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Brother Abu-'Ammar [Yasir 'Arafat] had a meeting 
today in Moscow with Russian Interior Minister Viktor Yerin at 
the Interior Ministry and briefed him on Palestinian 
preparations concerning the issue of setting up a Palestinian 
police and security service. The Russian minister showed his 
country's preparedness to offer all forms of support, aid, and 
assistance for the building of the structures of a Palestinian 
national security service and the setting up of a 
Palestinian-Russian joint committee for cooperation in national 
security and police. [passage omitted] 

