<F P=100> LEBANON </F>
<H3> <TI>   Hizballah Criticizes Israeli Presence at Oman Conference </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Hizballah Criticizes Israeli Presence at Oman Conference </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1904183494 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1530 GMT 19 Apr 
94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1904183494 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Hizballah issued a statement today saying that the 
participation of an official Zionist delegation in a conference 
on water held in Oman is a serious development that proves the 
Arab regimes' failure to observe the boycott of Israel. The 
statement notes that the willingness to cooperate with the 
Zionist enemy, which engages in the most brutal and criminal 
practices against the Lebanese and Palestinian people, is 
tantamount to encouraging such aggression and acquitting Israel 
of its dreadful crimes. 
  Hizballah warned that such cooperation will undermine all 
chances for regaining the usurped rights. 

</TEXT>

