<F P=100> ISRAEL </F>
<H3> <TI>   Shin Bet Head Warns of Chaos After IDF Pullout </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Shin Bet Head Warns of Chaos After IDF Pullout </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1804073794 Tel Aviv YEDI'OT AHARONOT in Hebrew 18 Apr 94 p 
7 </F>

<F P=103> TA1804073794 </F>
<F P=104>  Tel Aviv YEDI'OT AHARONOT </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by Smadar Peri and Shim'on Schiffer] </F>
  [Excerpt] "Chaos is expected in the Gaza Strip immediately 
after the IDF [Israel Defense Forces] leaves the region and 
hands it over to the PLO." This assessment was made by the head 
of the Shin Bet at yesterday's cabinet session. 
  The Shin Bet head anticipates that during the initial period 
after the IDF pullout, we will witness internecine massacres 
among the Palestinians. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

