<H3> <TI>   League Chief: No Romanian Meeting With Israelis Set </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    League Chief: No Romanian Meeting With Israelis Set </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1904164194 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1430 GMT 19 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC1904164194 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 19 Apr (MENA)--Arab League Secretary General 
Dr. 'Ismat 'Abd-al-Majid has denied that he will meet with any 
Israeli official during his visit to Romania, which will begin 
tomorrow. He was answering a question from MENA on press 
reports suggesting that he was likely to meet with the Israeli 
delegation participating in the annual meeting of the forum on 
political and democratic prospects in the world that will be 
held in Bucharest. 

