<H3> <TI>   Saddam Receives Yemeni Envoy, Message From President </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Saddam Receives Yemeni Envoy, Message From President </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN1704131994 Baghdad INA in Arabic 1134 GMT 17 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> JN1704131994 </F>
