<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Islamic Resistance has declared that the Martyr 
Muhammad Darwish Group launched a direct assault at 1830 today 
against an Israeli patrol composed of two personnel carriers, a 
Merkava tank, 13 infantry personnel, and a security vehicle on 
the 'Alman road, using various types of machine guns and 
rockets. A personnel carrier was burned out and its five crew 
members were killed or wounded and the security vehicle was hit. 
There were other casualties among the patrol personnel. 
Ambulances were seen rushing to the scene to evacuate the 
casualties. 
  Agent Lahd's [South Lebanese Army] radio reported the 
operation and that one soldier was wounded. 

</TEXT>

