<H3> <TI>   Grenades Explode in Cairo; 2 Injured </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Grenades Explode in Cairo; 2 Injured </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2104095894 Cairo MENA in Arabic 0854 GMT 21 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2104095894 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 21 Apr (MENA)--A hand grenade placed by 
unidentified people outside a shop on al-'Ishrin Street in the 
'Ayn Shams neighborhood of Cairo went off this morning. 
According to initial reports, the explosion left two people 
slightly wounded. They were taken to the hospital for treatment. 
The explosion also caused damage to the front of the house and 
shop. Security commanders and various investigation organs 
proceeded to the site of the explosion. 

</TEXT>

