  [Text] The prime minister, Mr. Narasimha Rao, today 
reiterated that the [Nuclear] Nonproliferation Treaty [NPT] 
should be nondiscriminatory and have universal application. 
During his talks with the visiting Ukrainian foreign minister, 
Mr. Anatoliy Maksymovych Zlenko, who called on him, Mr. Rao said 
